metadata.name: Capuensli #1
metadata.description:
The first capricorn by the famous Swiss artist Capuensli is now listed. This is the very first NFT by Capuensli & the future holder will also have the option to burn the NFT and request the physical Artwork #1 for an additional charge of 3 ETH.

Official website of CAPUENSLI: http://www.capuensli.ch/
